resources.name: conv_pipe.cl:747 (z_buffer)
details: Number of banks: 4 (banked on lowest dimension)

Total replication: 7
- Replicated 7 times to efficiently support multiple simultaneous workgroups. This replication resulted in no increase in actual block RAM usage.
Running memory at 2x clock to support more concurrent ports

Additional information: Requested size 261 bytes, implemented size 3584 bytes, replicated 7 times total, stallable, 5 reads and 6 writes. - Reduce the number of write accesses or fix banking to make this memory system stall-free. - Replicated 7 times to efficiently support multiple simultaneous workgroups. This replication resulted in no increase in actual block RAM usage. - Banked on lowest dimension into 4 separate banks. - See Best Practices Guide: Local Memory for more information.
